name: Cannalope Kush
description: Cannalope Kush from DNA Genetics mixes the powerful effects of OG #18 with the sweet fruity flavors of Cannalope Haze. Though it is sativa-dominant, many enjoy the balancing act of the underlying indica influence. This hybrid delivers a pleasant light smoke with woody undertones alongside an energetic burst of cerebral activity and euphoria.
